      "date": "2013-04-07 14:00:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a67c660c-9f87-11e2-86dc-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  4 tests failed: runtests, sanity-quota, replay-ost-single, recovery-small.",
